metadata.name: Bilnd Patron 2023 #1/10
metadata.description:
As a Bilnd Patron NFT holder, you will receive the following benefits:

• 3 unique 1/1 NFTs  
• A minimum of 3 edition airdrops  
• Access to a private discord server  
• Behind-the-scenes content  
• Q&A sessions  
• Coffee table book that documents the year

The Bilnd Patron 2023 NFT token runs 01/01/2023 - 31/12/2023
